      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i thought more water was good for lithium?? if i'm drinking more, won't that flush it out and stop the side effects? i feel like i'm just overreacting and if i just stay hydrated it'll be fine. plus my hands aren't like vibrating or anything, just a little tremor when i hold a fork. it's probably just my body getting used to it while i wait for my next checkup in a few weeks, right?",
